'''''The Empire Strikes Back Monthly'' 157''' is the one hundred fifty-seventh issue of the ''[[The Empire Strikes Back Monthly]]'' series of comic reprints, published in [[May]] [[1982]].

This issue includes one of the few original comic stories in the series, "[[The Flight of the Falcon]]". It was later reprinted and colorized in ''[[Classic Star Wars: Devilworlds]]'' [[Classic Star Wars: Devilworlds|1]].

